<doc id="1217172" wikidata="Q670368" url="?curid=1217172" title="Live... With a Little Help from Our Friends">
<text>Live... With a Little Help from Our Friends is a live recording of Gov&#x27;t Mule&#x27;s 1998 New Year&#x27;s Eve concert at The Roxy in Atlanta, Georgia. It was released as a 4-CD set &quot;Collector&#x27;s Edition&quot; and as two separate albums.

==Track listing==

