<doc id="1217231" wikidata="Q5600957" url="?curid=1217231" title="Greatest Hits, Vol. 1 (Blue Rodeo album)">
<text>Greatest Hits, Vol. 1 is a 2001 greatest hits album by Blue Rodeo. It was released in the United States in 2004.

==Track listing==
